description:
This is a 13 minute workout called 'Stretching Exercises for Bedtime - Relaxing Routine before Sleep or Anytime to Feel Better' from the channel SeniorShape Fitness.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Sleep Prep and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
